Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.35,0:03:44.10,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}于是牵住了伙伴的手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.81,0:03:50.03,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}这样的话将永远
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.28,0:03:54.99,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}活在童年无忧的时光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.99,0:04:02.66,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}无论如何都想要告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.08,0:04:08.80,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}伙伴们曾牵在一起的手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.21,0:04:15.47,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}已变得七零八落
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.47,0:04:19.39,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}一个个渐渐离去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.39,0:04:26.02,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}向着那苏醒之日
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.48,0:04:35.53,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}迈开脚步毅然前进
